#   Name      Mainworld name
#   Ix {+-n}  Importance Extension
#   Ex (RLI+-E)  Economic: Resources Labor Infrastructure Efficiency
#   Cx [HASS] Cultural: Homogeneity Acceptance Strangeness Symbols
